{"type":"message","id":"56b1201a","parentId":"d53f7398","timestamp":"2026-03-20T02:39:54.163Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这些文件是 Whisper 语音识别生成的输出文件。当我运行 whisper 命令时，它会在当前工作目录生成多种格式的输出文件：\n- .json - JSON格式的完整转录结果\n- .srt - 字幕格式\n- .tsv - 制表符分隔格式\n- .txt - 纯文本格式\n- .vtt - WebVTT字幕格式\n\n这些文件是用语音识别时产生的临时文件，可以清理掉。","thinkingSignature":"da254e4bfa5a0d80e23c6444ea27f3ff8249fe24e919d2e09e42cecf1255363f"},{"type":"text","text":"这些是 **Whisper 语音识别生成的输出文件**！\n\n每次运行 whisper 命令时，会自动生成以下格式的文件（以音频文件名为前缀）：\n\n| 文件类型 | 说明 |\n|---------|------|\n| `.txt` | 纯文本转录 |\n| `.json` | 完整转录结果（含时间戳） |\n| `.srt` | 字幕格式 |\n| `.vtt` | WebVTT字幕格式 |\n| `.tsv` | 制表符分隔格式 |\n\n这些是临时文件，可以用以下命令清理：\n\n```bash\nrm -f /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-test/*.txt /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-test/*.json /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-test/*.srt /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-test/*.vtt /home/robot/.openclaw/workspace-test/*.tsv\n```\n\n需要我帮您清理吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":48576,"output":288,"cacheRead":16063,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":64927,"cost":{"input":0.014572799999999999,"output":0.0003456,"cacheRead":0.00048188999999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.015400289999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1773974383204}}
